DENORMOLIZATION 
Scenario
In an analytics dashboard, frequent joins between sales, customer_info, and products will cause performance issues. 
Denormalizing helps reduce joins and improve read speed.

Denormalized Table:
CREATE TABLE denormalized_sales (
    sales_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    customer_id INT,
    full_name VARCHAR(120),
    location VARCHAR(90),
    product_id INT,
    product_name VARCHAR(120),
    price FLOAT,
    total_sales FLOAT
);




